*-------------------------------
*   CCC.DOC
*-------------------------------
*   CCC = Color Change Command
*-------------------------------

    CCC is a utility which changes screen colors
    for foreground, background, border(*),
    by command line.

    syntax : ccc f=nn,b=nn,e=nn

    where f = foreground
    where b = background
    where e = edge (border)

    and

    nn = 00 - 15


    if no command line is present;
    the default is:

    yellow foreground
    brown background
    brown edge

*----------------------------------------------------
    Color Chart

  Black    = 00   Light Black    = 08
  Blue     = 01   Light Blue     = 09
  Green    = 02   Light Green    = 10
  Cyan     = 03   Light Cyan     = 11
  Red      = 04   Light Red      = 12
  Magenta  = 05   Light Magenta  = 13
  Brown    = 06   Light Brown    = 14     ( Yellow )
  White    = 07   Light White    = 15
*----------------------------------------------------

  (*) = except on ega, vga, etc.

